# Engine Estrutura
## Roadmap v1.0 — Jun 2026

---

## Stack Tecnológica

```
Linguagem:      C++20 (core) + Python 3 (ferramentas)
Render:         Vulkan 1.3 / DX12 Ultimate / Metal (via bgfx ou The-Forge)
Física:         Jolt Physics (MIT)
ECS:            EnTT (MIT)
Áudio:          MiniAudio (MIT)
UI Editor:      Dear ImGui (MIT)
Asset Pipeline: Python 3
Hot Reload:     Live++ / C++ dll swap
Build:          CMake 3.20+
Licença:        MIT (engine própria, sem royalties)
```

---

## Estrutura de Diretórios

```
Engine/
├── core/
│   ├── math/          Cry_Math_SSE.h (SIMD)
│   ├── memory/        CryPool, BucketAllocator, STLPoolAllocator
│   ├── jobs/          JobManager lock-free queue
│   ├── platform/      Threads, atomics, platform defines
│   ├── console/       CVar system (IConsole.h)
│   └── streaming/     Time-sliced streaming
├── physics/           CryPhysics headers (referência) → Jolt Physics
├── render/
│   └── svo/           SVO Global Illumination (portar D3D11→Vulkan)
├── animation/
│   ├── statemachine/  NOSSA Animation State Machine ★
│   ├── skeleton/      ISkeletonAnim, layers, blending
│   ├── ik/            LimbIK, LookIK, AimIK, FeetLock
│   └── blendspace/    ParametricSampler 1D/2D/3D
├── editor/            Plugin EditorAnimationStateMachine
├── tools/             Python scripts, asset pipeline
├── thirdparty/
│   ├── EnTT/          ECS library
│   ├── JoltPhysics/   Physics engine
│   ├── bgfx/          Render abstraction
│   ├── imgui/         Editor UI
│   └── miniaudio/     Audio engine
├── .roadmap           Este arquivo
└── README.md          Documentação
```

